Third-party attributions
------------------------------------------------------------------------

This product, when deployed, queries and/or displays data from the
following third-party sources. Each carries the attribution and licensing
obligations summarised below. See docs/LICENSING.md for full details.

* OpenStreetMap contributors — map data licensed under the Open Database
  License (ODbL). https://www.openstreetmap.org/copyright

* Mapillary — street-level imagery licensed under CC BY-SA 4.0. Imagery
  displayed in the UI is attributed in place. https://www.mapillary.com/

* OpenCorporates — company registry data licensed under ODbL with the
  "Powered by OpenCorporates" attribution requirement.
  https://opencorporates.com/

* OpenRouteService — routing and isochrones, free tier with API key.
  Attribution displayed where routing results are shown.
  https://openrouteservice.org/

* crt.sh (Sectigo) — public certificate transparency logs.
  https://crt.sh/

* Internet Archive Wayback Machine — public web archive data, attribution
  requested. https://archive.org/

Aggregated and derived information is exposed to downstream consumers
through Joblantern's MCP servers; bulk redistribution of upstream data
is not performed.
